title: Totally Killer
plot: Totally Killer: Directed by Nahnatchka Khan. With Kiernan Shipka, Olivia Holt, Charlie Gillespie, Lochlyn Munro. When the infamous "Sweet Sixteen Killer" returns 35 years after his first murder spree to claim another victim, 17-year-old Jamie accidentally travels back in time to 1987, determined to stop the killer before he can start.
